# Godot's own editor cache for the test-harness project.godot at repo root
# (added so the addon has somewhere to boot for local testing / CI's
# headless smoke-boot check — see test/run_tests.gd and
# .github/workflows/test.yml). Never committed, regenerated on any boot.
.godot/

# No dot-prefixed folder is ever checked in to this repo (IDE project files, local agent tool
# state, whatever creates it). Only .github/ is exempted, since its workflow files are real,
# load-bearing repo infrastructure, not local tool state.
.*/
!/.github/
!/.github/**
